      "side": 1,
      "message": "Runtime-enforced rules are tricky, see: Making interfaces hard to misuse.  What do you think about:\n\nmessage Target {\n  string host \u003d 1;\n  // If empty, target applies to all projects on host.\n  repeated string project \u003d 2;\n}\nrepeated Target target \u003d 1;",
